🎯 Purpose of Section 1: Executive Summary

The Executive Summary is the “elevator pitch” of the manual. It must let senior leadership (steering committee, customer sponsors, delivery leadership) quickly grasp the core rationale, challenges, structure, and promises of this manual — in a way that earns their confidence and encourages them to lean in.

It’s not just a summary of topics; it’s a narrative invitation into the manual’s worldview and value.

⸻

