Element	What to Communicate	Wisdom / Coaching Layer
Opening Hook / Problem Statement	The fundamental gap in enterprise delivery (e.g. large programs collapse because rules are invisible and accountability is ambiguous)	VP Insight — a memorable line reflecting experience
