🧭 Narrative Flow & Composition
	1.	Hook + Context — a vivid problem or scenario that immediately resonates with enterprise stakeholders
	2.	Core Tensions — frame the delivery challenge as a landscape of trade-offs
	3.	Offer of this Manual — what you’ll help the reader with (not universally, but in context)
	4.	Roadmap / Structure in Miniature — preview of major sections and how they link
	5.	Reader Guidance — how to read, how to use, what to prioritize
	6.	Commitment / Invitation — a call to treat this manual as a living guide

